FM 7 presets are live! I hope you’ll look at these before and afters examples, I spent a lot of time crafting them to work with Sony, Fuji, Canon, Leica, iPhone, and more - and I didn’t just test new cameras with new sensors. You can edit with them on any sort of device you have, mobile, tablet, desktop/laptop, and I’ll just say that after spending a year working on them - they are very well done.  Link in bio, you’ll see they are quite different from the previous releases ❤️

One of the biggest things about FM 7 presets is that they make photos from older cameras keep up with brand new cameras. I’ve been shooting a lot on my old 5D and 5D II and they match up just great with my R5. It’s not a canon specific thing, these presets are just built to maximize image quality. You can get them now via my bio. Thank you all for the support 🌵

I edited every single one of these images on my iPhone just now in about five minutes total all using my new FM 7 presets - the ability to make such quick and advanced adjustments on your phone is huge. Available now via my page 🙌
